room_title: Escape room "The Legend of Atlantis" by Gatlin's Escape Games in Pigeon Forge
room_description:
World famous explorer Hathaway Wren made the discovery of a lifetime. Several weeks have passed since Wrenâ€™s groundbreaking transmission, and all attempts to contact him have proven futile.
